## AI-First Approach

This project is developed with an `AI-First` approach; meaning the code structure is designed in a way that makes it easier for AI tools to review, understand, and apply changes.

And this approach is such that the relevant content and required information are kept in a single file and not spread across different files, so that AI can understand the content and structure of that file sufficiently by reading even one file.

Features of this approach:

- Keeping related information close to the logic of the same file
- Reducing unnecessary dependencies between files
- Followable structure for faster code review
- Ability to understand main parts of the project by sending a file or limited set of files to AI tools
- Reducing the need for Agent to make small changes or review independent sections

