## Installation and Setup

### Prerequisites

- Node.js version `20.x` or higher
- npm version `9.x` or higher

### Project Installation
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/andisheSazan.git
cd andisheSazan

npm install

### Environment Variables

The required environment variables for the project are pre-defined and currently there is no need to change the `.env` file.

### Running the Project

bash
npm run start

### Running the English Version

bash
npm run start:en

### Creating a New Admin

bash
npm run createAdmin <adminName> <password>

Example:

bash
npm run createAdmin admin password123

