| File | Responsibility |
| :--- | :--- |
| `index.js` | Application entry point, Express setup, and main routes |
| `logger.js` | Winston configuration for logging to file and console |
| `config.js` | General settings, paths, Rate Limiting, and Helmet |
| `routes/admin.js` | Authentication and admin panel login |
| `routes/adminProducts.js` | Product CRUD operations |
| `routes/adminBlogs.js` | Blog CRUD operations |
| `routes/adminFaq.js` | FAQ CRUD operations |
| `routes/adminImages.js` | Image upload and deletion |
| `routes/api.js` | Public API for products and blogs |